{
  "stem": "17526.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And miraculously, miraculously they let me go.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they have shot and killed people for less [? offenses. ?] And this was a real sort of thing to-- to suspect, a suspicious thing.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I escaped that one, but I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he really saved me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The judenalteste, the head of the Jewish inmates, he really somehow saved me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Coming back from the [GERMAN] every day, you would be counted.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And inadvertently, every once in a while, somebody will be missing, somebody would escape.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they later on ordained that if anybody escapes from a certain group, the whole group will be shot.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And one time, they shot 20 people from this column.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "A guy was missing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "This is in order to teach everybody a lesson to watch one for another.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because if you see that he is trying to escape, you better watch, otherwise you will be shot.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "One time they shot 20 people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the-- standing there after a whole day's work in [GERMAN] plant and after marching back after being starved, literally starved out, we had to stay in line to be counted many times for hours at a time.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "When you finally were dismissed, then you were reporting standing in line to get your dinner for the day.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "The dinner consisted-- everybody had a bowl, a tin bowl, and you would get a-- a-- a bowl of soup, which was spinach most of the time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the spinach was just with hot water without clean-- being cleaned, with the sand in it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And you would get a slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The loaves of bread were about this big.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
